{
  "stem": "888.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in that particular sense, I think we felt quite a great loss, you know, as far as-- that we are, you understand, sort of surrounded by, by enemies.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Did you spend any time thinking about missing your parents?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We thought about them all the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All the time.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, what happened, and what-- how are they faring, and, you know, the kids, and everything like that, you know?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And of course, we had our nightmares, you know, and things like that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Occasionally.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Occasionally.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I might be dreaming of being, you know, chased, like, or something.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Or being persecuted, or something like that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean-- and of course, you know, like, like I say, I always try to put things like that out of my mind.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well-- well, first of all, you know, that you survived.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[CRYING] And then they didn't.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[CRYING]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course, you know, like my brother, you know-- we were in the same bed together.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, and two weeks later, you know, just for sheer negligence-- you know, nobody-- nobody even looked at us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And not even gave us-- if we weren't able to, to help ourselves, you know, just give one another a little water or maybe just take a little towel, or whatever we had, to put on somebody's head that they shouldn't burn up from fever.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this was after, you know-- of course, a lot of people, I suppose, didn't want to catch the disease.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, it was a typhoid, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- So that's what you go back to the most?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, you know-- you know, after, you know, I was for seven years alone, after the war, until I got married.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
